dc_description_s: This data layer represents zoning for Polk County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, NPolk_Zoning_2018.gdbN. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are NPolk_General_2018N and NPolk_Shoreland_2018N. [This dataset designates the zoning district for geographical areas in Polk County. The data set is a compilation of multiple internal data sets including 'ZoningComp', 'ZoningShoreland', 'ZoneGenPur', and 'ZoningWet'.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
